### Key Optimizations:
- Coalesced global memory access patterns
- Vectorized loads (float4/half2/uint4) where applicable
- FP32 accumulation for FP16 inputs to maintain numerical stability
- Row-wise parallelization with 256 threads per block
- Efficient handling of edge cases and remainder elements

